data.description: Welcome to 12833 Medford Rd in the Parkwood section of the Far Northeast. This beautiful townhome is ready for you to call home! Unpack and move right in!  As you enter the home, step right into your spacious living room, filled with natural light, which leads right into the dining room with open floor plan to the updated kitchen. The main floor is freshly painted.  This home features 3 spacious bedrooms with plenty of closet space and 1 1/2 bathrooms. Downstairs you will find a fully finished basement, laundry room, an updated half bathroom, inside garage access and plenty of storage. Step outside to your cozy backyard! Schedule your showing today. With limited inventory, you don't want to let this one slip away!
